{
  "stem": "1733.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 134.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then, during the day, when they had nothing to do with us, they made us carry stones up a hill.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then when the stones-- all the big stones were up the hill already, they made us carry it down and then carry it up again.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that was the form of exercise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But everybody was treated equally.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, it wasn't too bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then, from Nagybanya, we were there several weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Munka Szalot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "M-U-N-K-A, capital S-Z-A-L-O-T.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's close enough.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think I spelled it properly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were distinguished between the military and ourselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We did not have any uniforms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had our own clothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The only thing that we had to wear was the yellow armband on the left side.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were with Hungarian-- with the Hungarian Army-- under the Hungarian army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had the same officers as the regular army had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "From after basic training, we went to Budakalasz, which is a suburb of Budapest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And Budakalasz is spelled B-U-D-A, capital K-O-L-A-S-Z.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were stationed in a-- I don't know whether it was a school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I think it was a big saloon, a big area that was requisitioned to house the group that we were there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were involved in building antiaircraft installations.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were treated properly in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We worked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They fed us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were exercising.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I especially had a good-- a good job there, because I was working in the office, so I did not have to do any heavy labor.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I was helped by the office people that I was working with, which was civilians.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it wasn't bad until the end, when the Germans came over already.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
